channel.title: Dane Cook
channel.description:
Dane Cook is the sex bomb. He's a great comedian and I'd love to see one of his shows, and it just so happens, he's right here in Las Vegas December first! Now, this is three days from now. I just got news of this today! What the fuck! So I go to check out the tickets, and the only thing there that fitted what I wanted, was two 159 USD tickets! Retarded, so I guess I got fucked on this one. Hopefully he'll be here again some time.
Anyway, has anyone ever seen one of his shows, or just a good concert or stand-up comedy show?
